Plain-English summary
================================================================

YOU MAY:
  • Use Claude Radar for personal, educational, research, or any
    other non-commercial purpose
  • Modify, fork, and build derivative works on top of it
  • Share copies and modified versions, freely

YOU MUST:
  • Give appropriate credit — link back to the original repository
    (https://github.com/lemomo-ai/claude-radar) and name the author
  • Indicate clearly if you made changes
  • Apply the same NonCommercial restriction to any derivative work

YOU MAY NOT:
  • Use Claude Radar — or anything substantially derived from it —
    for commercial purposes without a separate commercial license

================================================================
Commercial use
================================================================

The following uses require a separate commercial license:

  • Bundling Claude Radar (or a derivative) into a paid product
    or service
  • Internal use in a for-profit organization that goes beyond
    individual employees evaluating their own sessions
  • Hosting Claude Radar as a paid SaaS or other paid offering
  • Selling reports, analyses, or aggregated insights produced
    using Claude Radar's scoring engine
  • Using Claude Radar's scoring or diagnosis output as part of
    a commercial assessment, certification, or coaching service

For commercial licensing — including pricing, terms, and any
custom arrangements — please contact:

    Leif Diao
    leifdiao@gmail.com
    https://github.com/lemomo-ai

